1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:13,000
 Biti kršćanin nije u stvari popis zadataka koje treba odraditi.

2
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:20,000
 Biti kršćanin je preobrazba moje osobe, mene osobno.

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
 Preobrazba u što?

4
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:26,000
 Što bi trebali postati?

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
 I kako će to izgledat?

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:50,000
 Mislim da smo i jako blagoslovljeni zbog ova dva sviljezačanstva koje smo čuli danas.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:01:04,000
 Želim pohvaliti i vodstvo ove konferencije koje razlučilo ova dva sviljezačanstva.

8
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:09,000
 Jer potpuno se uklapaju zajedno jedno s drugim.

9
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:19,000
 Svako od njih ima svoje putovanje, svoj put, ali je u stvari ista priča.

10
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:36,000
 Bog pronalazi nesavršeno ljudsko biće i Bog poziva to nesavršeno ljudsko biće da krenu zajedno u jednu avanturu.

11
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:40,000
 Ne razumijemo uvijek.

12
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:46,000
 Nikad ne učinimo baš onako kako to treba učiniti.

13
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:52,000
 Ali Bog strpljivo hoda zajedno s nama.

14
00:01:52,000 --> 00:02:00,000
 I Josip i Ivan su pričali o osobnoj slobodi.

15
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:08,000
 Pričali su o tome kako su trebali neke stvari pustiti i predati.

16
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:18,000
 Pričali su o tome kako su se boreli sa stvarima u lastitom srcu.

17
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:24,000
 Obe su pričali o tome kako ih je gospodin zaštitio.

18
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:28,000
 Ista je priča.

19
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:32,000
 I vi ste isto dio te priče.

20
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:42,000
 Ako razmotrite vidjet ćete elemente toga u svom životu već sada.

21
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:46,000
 Idemo nastaviti hodati u nadi.

22
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:52,000
 Jer Isus u istinu je gospodin.

23
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:57,000
 Jedna stvar koju sam čuo od obojice.

24
00:02:57,000 --> 00:03:03,000
 Bolje im je s Isusom nego bez Isusa.

25
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:09,000
 Ivan, you talked about a new vision, a new direction.

26
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:15,000
 Josip, you talked about a new mission, a new focus.

27
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:23,000
 One of the greatest gifts that Jesus the Lord will give you.

28
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:30,000
 He will give you a dream bigger than yourself.

29
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:36,000
 He will give you a vision that will stretch you.

30
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:39,000
 That will challenge you.

31
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:45,000
 And ultimately will make you a better man.

32
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,000
 I think we are all beginning to discover.

33
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:52,000
 Mislim da svi zajedno počinjemo otkrivat.

34
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:56,000
 Living only for ourself is a dead end street.

35
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:00,000
 Da je život samo za sebe put koji nema smisla.

36
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:08,000
 Mnogi problemi koje vidimo u svijetu upravo danas.

37
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:13,000
 Individuals are making themselves the center of the universe.

38
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:17,000
 Pojedinci čine sami sebe kao da su centar svijeta.

39
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:20,000
 And that is out of God's order.

40
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,000
 I to nije Božji red. To je izvan Božeg reda.

41
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:32,000
 Vidio sam jednu majicu na kojoj su pisala dva veoma važna pravila.

42
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,000
 Pravilo broj jedan.

43
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:38,000
 Postoji Bog.

44
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:41,000
 Pravilo broj dva.

45
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:44,000
 Ti nisi On.

46
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:49,000
 To su dva dobra pravila za život.

47
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:55,000
 Ono što su naša dva brata posjedočila danas.

48
00:04:55,000 --> 00:05:00,000
 Pričali su nam svoju priču.

49
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:06,000
 Stvari pričali su nam našu priču.

50
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:10,000
 Svi smo na istom putu.

51
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,000
 Izgledam mrvu drugačije.

52
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:18,000
 Heroj je isti.

53
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:24,000
 Glavni lik priče je isti.

54
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:29,000
 I na neki način putovanje je isto.

55
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:48,000
 Pogledajmo onda danas popodne kako Isus koji je gospodin želi promijeniti naš život na jedan dublji način.

56
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:58,000
 Rekao sam malo ranije danas da sad kada živimo pod Isusovim gospodstvom.

57
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:03,000
 Moramo pričati o gospodstvu.

58
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:09,000
 Moramo činiti njegova dijela.

59
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:19,000
 Ali možda ono najbitnije biti nešto drugo.

60
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:25,000
 Uzeće čovjeka koji smo sada.

61
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:35,000
 I učiniti nas najboljom verzijom nas osobno.

62
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,000
 U jednom smislu.

63
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:46,000
 St. Paul kaže da moramo umrijeti sami sebi.

64
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:50,000
 A na drugi način.

65
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:58,000
 Pravi mi zapravo oživljavamo.

66
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:08,000
 Pao je u stvari koristio ove reči.

67
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,000
 Uvijek umiremo.

68
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:21,000
 I uvijek u sebi nosimo uskrslo Krista, uskrsnuće koje je Kristim donio.

69
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:24,000
 To je paradoks.

70
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:27,000
 Ali to je istina.

71
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:36,000
 Bio sam jako dodirnut nadbiskup ovom propovijedi danas.

72
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:40,000
 i evanđeljem.

73
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:45,000
 Dođite svi vi koji ste umorni i opterečeni.

74
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,000
 Uzmite jara moj.

75
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:51,000
 I učite od mene.

76
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:57,000
 Brothers, what God wants to do is to actually change our nature.

77
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:02,000
 Braćo, što Bog zaista želi učiniti je promijeniti našu naravu.

78
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:11,000
 Biti kršćanin nije u stvari popis zadataka koje treba odraditi.

79
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:21,000
 Biti kršćanin je preobrazba moje osobe, mene osobno.

80
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:25,000
 Preobrazba u što?

81
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:28,000
 Što bi trebali postati?

82
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:31,000
 I kako će to izgledat?

83
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:48,000
 I postoje jedan kratki citat iz prve poslanice Ivana apostola.

84
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:53,000
 i Josip i ja smo o tome pričali prije koju minutu.

85
00:08:53,000 --> 00:09:02,000
 I tell you honestly, it is the hardest Bible passage for me to believe.

86
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:07,000
 I iskreno to je za mene citat koji mi je najteže povjerovati iz Biblije.

87
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:14,000
 Vjerujem u djevićansko za čeće i rođenje.

88
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:19,000
 Vjerujem da se Isus utjelovio.

89
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:26,000
 Vjerujem da je u istinu umro na križu i uskrsnuo od mrtvih.

90
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:34,000
 Isus je uzašao na nebo i uskoro će se vratiti.

91
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:37,000
 Vjerujem to u potpunosti, stvarno vjerujem.

92
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:43,000
 Dao sam svoj život za ta ovjerenja.

93
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:49,000
 Ali postoji jedan citat s kojim se dalje mučim.

94
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,000
 I ovdje je:

95
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:55,000
 "Brothers,

96
00:09:55,000 --> 00:10:00,000
 see with what love the Father has loved us."

97
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:04,000
 Pogledajte kako nas je Otac ljubio, kako nas Otac ljubi.

98
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:11,000
 U tome da se možemo zvati Djeca Božja.

99
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:14,000
 And yet, so we are.

100
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:17,000
 I u istinu to jesmo.

101
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:25,000
 Mi smo sada Božja djeca.

102
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:30,000
 Ono što ćemo postati

103
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:34,000
 još nam nije otkriveno.

104
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,000
 Ali,

105
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:40,000
 Slušajte ovo.

106
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:45,000
 Kada bude otkriveno,

107
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:50,000
 mi ćemo biti

108
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:57,000
 poput Njega.

109
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:00,000
 Boži plan je

110
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:03,000
 da jednog dana

111
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,000
 u budućnosti

112
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:11,000
 da vi budete poput Krista.

113
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:18,000
 Možete li to podnijeti?

114
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,000
 Ok, nema veze.

115
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,000
 Ok, nema veze.

116
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:31,000
 Te riječi uvijek uzdrmaju moj svijet.

117
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:34,000
 I can see that for Mother Teresa.

118
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:37,000
 Mogu to vidjeti za Majku Terezu.

119
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:40,000
 John Paul II being like Christ?

120
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
 Yeah, I can see that.

121
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,000
 Ivan Pao II je bio poput Krista

122
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,000
 i mogo bi to reći.

123
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,000
 I know a lot of you men.

124
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,000
 Znam mnogo vas.

125
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,000
 And I think you're

126
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,000
 a pretty good witness of Christ.

127
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:55,000
 I mislim da ste jako dobri svjedoci Krista.

128
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,000
 But then I look at myself.

129
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,000
 I onda pogledam sebe.

130
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,000
 I'm serious.

131
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:05,000
 It's a very great leap of faith for me.

132
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,000
 I ozbiljan sam kad kažem da je to

133
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,000
 veliki skok u vjeri za mene.

134
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:15,000
 Jer vidim svoje osobne grijehe.

135
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:18,000
 I see those dark places within my own heart

136
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,000
 that I would never talk about.

137
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:27,000
 I think of the stupid and selfish things I've done.

138
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:32,000
 People that have hurt.

139
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,000
 So for me to think someday

140
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:38,000
 I could even be close to Christ

141
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,000
 it's just too big of a gap.

142
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:49,000
 But that is what the scriptures say.

143
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:52,000
 Ali to je ono što Biblija kaže.

144
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:55,000
 So as a Catholic

145
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:58,000
 I'm obliged

146
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:02,000
 to believe in the teaching of the Catholic Church.

147
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:05,000
 Obavezan sam vjerovati u učiteljstvo

148
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,000
 i učenje katoličke crkve.

149
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:12,000
 When a priest is preparing the gifts for communion

150
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:16,000
 kada svećenici pripremaju darove za prinos

151
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:19,000
 he takes the bread and offers it.

152
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,000
 Uzimaju kruh i predaju ga.

153
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
 Prinose ga.

154
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,000
 And then he has the chalice

155
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
 onda uzme kalež

156
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:29,000
 and he pours a little wine in the chalice.

157
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
 Stavi malo vina u taj kalež.

158
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:34,000
 And then he pours a few drops of water in the chalice.

159
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:37,000
 I onda doda par kapi vode u tajisti kalež.

160
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,000
 And this is what he says.

161
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,000
 I ovo je ono što govori.

162
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:43,000
 through the mystery

163
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:47,000
 of the mingling of the water and wine

164
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,000
 mješanja vode i vina

165
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,000
 may we

166
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
 neka mi

167
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:57,000
 come to share in the divinity

168
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,000
 postanemo sudionici božanstva

169
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,000
 of Christ

170
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:03,000
 who humbled himself

171
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:06,000
 to share in our humanity.

172
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:11,000
 Koji se ponizio kako bi bio s nama u našem čovještvu.

173
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
 What does that mean?

174
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,000
 Što to znači?

175
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,000
 St. Thomas Aquinas says this.

176
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,000
 Sveti Thomas Aquinas kaže ovo.

177
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:24,000
 The proper effect of receiving the Eucharist

178
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:31,000
 is the divinization of men.

179
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:37,000
 Is that even possible?

180
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
 Je li to uopće moguće?

181
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,000
 Now to be clear

182
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
 we are not saying

183
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:45,000
 we're going to like replace God.

184
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
 Ne kažemo da budemo jasni

185
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
 zamijeniti Boga.

186
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
 But there's gonna be some

187
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,000
 some kind of a

188
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,000
 of a mystical union.

189
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,000
 Ali da će bit neko

190
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:58,000
 mistično jedinstvo, zajedništvo.

191
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:01,000
 That we will be so close with him.

192
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,000
 Da ćemo bit toliko blizu njemu.

193
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:16,000
 da će biti neko njegovo manifestacija njega u našem životu.

194
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,000
 Sometimes in the Bible it says

195
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:23,000
 that gold is refined seven times.

196
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:27,000
 Na jednom mjestu u Bibliji kaže da se zlato pročišćava sedam puta.

197
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:42,000
 Danas čistoća zlata se može provjeriti kemijskim testiranjem.

198
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:46,000
 Ali u biblijska vremena

199
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:51,000
 morali su koristiti neke jednostavnije metode.

200
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:56,000
 They would take the ore, the rough rocks, and pound them.

201
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:59,000
 Uzeli bi kamen i udarali bi ih.

202
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:03,000
 And then they would put it in a bowl that could take the heat.

203
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:07,000
 I onda bi stavili u neku posudu koja mogla izdržati toplinu.

204
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
 A crucible.

205
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
 A crucible.

206
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,000
 Yeah.

207
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,000
 Crucible.

208
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:18,000
 And when they put this bowl in the furnace,

209
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,000
 kad su stavili tu posudu u peć,

210
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:24,000
 the ore would begin to melt from the heat.

211
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:28,000
 Zlato bi se počelo topiti, ta smjesa bi se počela topiti.

212
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:36,000
 Kovač bi uzeo van tu posudu.

213
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:39,000
 And all the debris would have risen to the top.

214
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:43,000
 I sav otpad bi se dignuo na vrh.

215
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:46,000
 He would scrape out the debris.

216
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:49,000
 Uzeo bi, postrugao bi taj otpad.

217
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,000
 And push the ball back into the fire.

218
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:53,000
 I vratio nazad posudu u vatru.

219
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:58,000
 U Bibliji kaže da je to činilo sedam puta.

220
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:02,000
 And the number seven doesn't necessarily mean one, two, three.

221
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:07,000
 It doesn't mean a number.

222
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:12,000
 It's a sense of completion.

223
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:18,000
 So maybe for some of us that's seven times.

224
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:22,000
 Maybe for some of us it's 700 times.

225
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:25,000
 But the gold goes into the fire.

226
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,000
 Ali zlato ide u vatru.

227
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,000
 It comes out of the fire.

228
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,000
 Vraća se nazad iz vatre.

229
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,000
 The master scrapes off the debris.

230
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,000
 Učitelj makne otpad.

231
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,000
 And pushes it back in the fire.

232
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,000
 I vraća natrag u vatru.

233
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:42,000
 And how does he know when the gold is pure?

234
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:45,000
 I kako zna kada je zlato čisto?

235
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:50,000
 After several efforts at this.

236
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:53,000
 Nakon nekoliko ponavljanja takvih.

237
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:58,000
 The master will pull the bowl of liquid gold out of the furnace.

238
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:04,000
 Učitelj će izvadit posudu koja je puna čistog tekućeg zlata.

239
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:08,000
 And he will stand over it and look directly down into the bowl.

240
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:11,000
 Stajeće za njej pogled točno u nju.

241
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:15,000
 He knows it's perfectly pure.

242
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 Znače da je savršeno čista.

243
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:23,000
 When he sees his own reflection coming back to him in the liquid gold.

244
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:27,000
 Kada u tom tekućem zlatu vidi svoj odraz.

245
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,000
 What does Saint Paul mean?

246
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:31,000
 Što je Sveti Pavao mislio?

247
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,000
 It's no longer I who live.

248
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,000
 Ne živim više ja.

