00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,000
 But it's Christ who lives in me.

250
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:39,000
 Nego Krist živi u meni.

251
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:43,000
 Today we're celebrating the feast of Saint Francis.

252
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:46,000
 Danas slavimo spomen dan Svetog Franje.

253
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,000
 Some called him the little Christ.

254
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:51,000
 Neki su ga zvali malim Kristom.

