363
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:47,000
 So let's take a little look today at how does this character get transformed.

364
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:53,000
 Ajmo pogledat danas malo kako to da se taj karakter može se mijenja i preobražava.

365
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:56,000
 Let's go back to the Archbishop's homily.

366
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:58,000
 Vratimo se na nadbiskupovu propovijetu.

367
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:02,000
 Take my yoke upon you.

368
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:04,000
 Uzmite jara moj na sebe.

369
