 i počnite hodati.

604
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:50,000
 ne mora vam se sviđati.

605
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,000
 ne morate čak biti ni dobri u tome.

606
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,000
 ne morate čak biti ni dobri u tome.

