00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,000
 ne morate čak biti ni dobri u tome.

608
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:57,000
 samo počnite hodati.

609
00:42:58,000 --> 00:43:03,000
 svaki put kad bi se susrao s nekom osobom

